#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "&step; is an interactive physical simulator."
msgstr "&step; je interaktivni fizikalni simulator."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "&step; features:"
msgstr "&step; zmožnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Classical mechanical simulation in two dimensions"
msgstr "Klasična mehanska simulacija v dveh dimenzijah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Particles, springs with damping, gravitational and coulomb forces"
msgstr "Delci, vzmeti z dušenjem, gravitacijske in coulombove sile"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rigid bodies"
msgstr "Toga telesa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collision detection (currently only discrete) and handling"
msgstr "Zaznavanje trkov (trenutno samo diskretnih) in upravljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Soft (deformable) bodies simulated as user-editable particles-springs "
"system, sound waves"
msgstr ""
"Mehka (deformabilna) telesa, simulirana kot sistem delcev-vzmeti, ki ga "
"lahko ureja uporabnik, zvočni valovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Molecular dynamics (currently using Lennard-Jones potential): gas and "
"liquid, condensation and evaporation, calculation of macroscopic quantities "
"and their variances"
msgstr ""
"Molekularna dinamika (trenutno uporablja Lennard-Jonesov potencial): plin in "
"tekočina, kondenzacija in izhlapevanje, izračun makroskopskih količin in "
"njihovih varianc"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Units conversion and expression calculation: you can enter something like "
"<quote>(2 days + 3 hours) * 80 km/h</quote> and it will be accepted as "
"distance value (requires libqalculate)"
msgstr ""
"Pretvorba enot in izračun izraza: vnesete lahko nekaj takega <quote>(2 dni + "
"3 ure) * 80 km/h</quote> in to bo sprejeto kot vrednost razdalje (zahteva "
"libqalculate)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Errors calculation and propagation: you can enter values like <quote>1.3 ± "
"0.2</quote> for any property and errors for all dependent properties will be "
"calculated using statistical formulas"
msgstr ""
"Izračun in širjenje napak: vnesete lahko vrednosti, kot je <quote>1,3 ± 0,2</"
"quote> za katero koli lastnost in napake za vse odvisne lastnosti bodo "
"izračunane z uporabo statističnih formul"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Solver error estimation: errors introduced by the solver is calculated and "
"added to user-entered errors"
msgstr ""
"Ocena napake reševalnika: napake, ki jih vnese reševalnik, se izračunajo in "
"dodajo napakam, ki jih vnese uporabnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several different solvers: up to 8th order, explicit and implicit, with or "
"without adaptive timestep (most of the solvers require GSL library)"
msgstr ""
"Več različnih reševalnikov: do 8. reda, eksplicitni in implicitni, z ali "
"brez prilagodljivega časovnega koraka (večina reševalnikov zahteva knjižnico "
"GSL)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Controller tool to easily control properties during simulation (even with "
"custom keyboard shortcuts)"
msgstr ""
"Orodje krmilnika za enostavno upravljanje lastnosti med simulacijo (tudi z "
"bližnjicami na tipkovnici po meri)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tools to visualize results: graph, meter, tracer"
msgstr "Orodja za vizualizacijo rezultatov: graf, merilnik, sledilnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context information for all objects, integrated wikipedia browser"
msgstr "Kontekstne informacije za vse predmete, integriran brskalnik wikipedia"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Collection of example experiments, more can be downloaded with &knewstuff;3"
msgstr "Zbirka primerov poskusov, več jih lahko prenesete z &knewstuff;3"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integrated tutorials"
msgstr "Integrirane vadnice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &step;"
msgstr "Uporaba &step;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&step; simulates a physical world. The main part of &step; (1) is the world "
"scene in the center of &step; main window where you first place physical "
"objects and where you see the simulation. On the left of this scene a "
"palette (2) let you choose your physical objects. You can freely move this "
"palette anywhere on your desktop by dragging the title bar. On the right of "
"the scene you can see the current world description (3), its properties (4), "
"some help to explain some words (5) and the history of the current world "
"(6). Each of those panels can be placed elsewhere on your screen by dragging "
"the title bar."
msgstr ""
"&step; simulira fizikalni svet. Glavni del &step; (1) je svetovna scena v "
"središču &step; glavno okno, kamor najprej postavite fizične objekte in kjer "
"vidite simulacijo. Na levi strani tega prizora vam paleta (2) omogoča izbiro "
"fizičnih objektov. To paleto lahko prosto premikate kamor koli na namizju "
"tako, da povlečete naslovno vrstico. Na desni strani prizora si lahko "
"ogledate trenutni opis sveta (3), njegove lastnosti (4), pomoč pri razlagi "
"nekaterih besed (5) in zgodovino trenutnega sveta (6). Vsako od teh plošč "
"lahko postavite drugam na zaslonu tako, da povlečete naslovno vrstico."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &step; when you start it for the first time"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &step; ko ga zaženete prvič"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "&step; Main Window"
msgstr "&step; Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To help you get started, &step; integrates a series of tutorials which "
"easily teach you how to build an experiment. Please see step by step to "
"start with the first tutorial."
msgstr ""
"Za lažji začetek &step; vključuje niz vadnic, ki vas preprosto naučijo, kako "
"narediti poskus. Oglejte si korak za korakom, da začnete s prvo vadnico."

